<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading"><br>Moral of the Story</h2>



<p data-slot-rendered-content=3D"true">Financial stuff isn=E2=80=99t comfor=
table. For most people, it=E2=80=99s not fun to talk about or focus on. Peo=
ple would rather discuss their sex lives, therapy, or medication at the din=
ner table than their finances. When I was a financial planner, it was a jok=
e with many of my clients that I knew them better than their own families d=
id; because once you open up about money, everything else follows.</p>
