<p>Today, I still don=E2=80=99t make a huge income. I certainly can=E2=80=
=99t afford the sort of lifestyle that some of my travel colleagues (many o=
f whom I=E2=80=99ve interviewed in my <a href=3D"https://www.theprofessiona=
lhobo.com/category/financial-case-studies/" data-modified-href=3D"https://w=
ww.theprofessionalhobo.com/category/financial-case-studies">Financial Case =
Study series</a>) can. But <strong>I enjoy a quality of life that is commen=
surate with my income, and enjoy it I do. </strong></p>



<p><em>THIS. This, is financially sustainable travel.</em></p>


